社會契約論 #盧梭 #官商鄉黑 #德性倫理學<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/116498648885670/posts/536053196930211?s=563194951&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F116498648885670%2Fposts%2F536053196930211%3Fs%3D563194951%26sfns%3Dmo&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=a4c19307\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/116498648885670/posts/536053196930211?s=563194951&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:37:03.000Z","msg":"同意呢個說法<br />\n<br />\nFF集中營<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357881</a>"},{"pid":"b93f7db528090b1dae4bfa94559857ad7dfbec3e","tid":1355423,"uid":43098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:41:40.000Z","msg":"雖然社會學既理論好多時都只係得個講 <br />\n但大家都可以認識一下 再知道更多自己既權益！"},{"pid":"2c1c87ccaa7ffd90437122c25fc5071a24cc8948","tid":1355423,"uid":43098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:17:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a9db848af45adb1a4197e6628e6ced907bcb4e6c","tid":1355423,"uid":178205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:23:34.000Z","msg":"聞誅一夫 不聞弒君"},{"pid":"f61066c2040688cce30f22a31f57ebed9f85d638","tid":1355423,"uid":43098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:31:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1469ef44e327c3356a5ce59f0f01bef3c33408f0","tid":1355423,"uid":43098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:21:33.000Z","msg":"PUSH"}]}